msgid "# Feature × Feature"
msgstr "# 功能 × 功能"

msgid ""
"The table below shows mutually exclusive features and the support on Ascend "
"hardware, extended from the [vLLM "
"table](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/#feature-x-feature)."
msgstr ""
"下表展示了互斥功能及其在昇腾硬件上的支持情况，该表是对 [vLLM "
"表格](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/features/#feature-x-feature) 的扩展。"

msgid "The symbols used have the following meanings:"
msgstr "所用符号的含义如下："

msgid ""
"- ✅ = Full compatibility\n"
"- 🟠 = Partial compatibility\n"
"- ❌ = No compatibility\n"
"- ❔ = Unknown or TBD"
msgstr ""
"- ✅ = 完全兼容\n"
"- 🟠 = 部分兼容\n"
"- ❌ = 不兼容\n"
"- ❔ = 未知或待定"

msgid ""
"- <sup>1</sup> Only dcp supports dp while pcp does not support dp.\n"
"- <sup>2</sup> Flashcomm is only enabled on the prefill stage.\n"
"- <sup>3</sup> Layer sharding is only enabled on the prefill stage.\n"
"- <sup>4</sup> Lmhead TP is only enabled in the pure dp scenarios.\n"
"- <sup>5</sup> MLAPO is only supported on the decode stage."
msgstr ""
"- <sup>1</sup> 仅 dcp 支持 dp，pcp 不支持 dp。\n"
"- <sup>2</sup> Flashcomm 仅在预填充阶段启用。\n"
"- <sup>3</sup> 层分片仅在预填充阶段启用。\n"
"- <sup>4</sup> Lmhead TP 仅在纯 dp 场景下启用。\n"
"- <sup>5</sup> MLAPO 仅在解码阶段支持。"

